"""

import pandas as pd
import json

# Parse the table
df = pd.read_html('table')[0]

# Find the row with the lowest score against Philadelphia 76ers
min_score_row = df.loc[(df['opponent'] == 'Philadelphia 76ers') & (df['score'].str[3:].astype(int) == min(df['score'].str[3:].astype(int)))][['score', 'record']].sort_values('score').iloc[0]

# Extract the relevant data
relevant_cells = [
    {'row_index': min_score_row.name[1], 'column_name': 'score'},
    {'row_index': min_score_row.name[1], 'column_name': 'record'}
]

# Create the response JSON
response_json = json.dumps({
  "answer": "TRUE" if df.loc[(df['opponent'] == 'Philadelphia 76ers') & (df['score'].str[3:].astype(int) == min(df['score'].str[3:].astype(int)))].shape[0] > 0 else "FALSE",
  "relevant_cells": relevant_cells
})

print(response_json)
